data.description: Lender Incentives/Concessions Available for Buyers. Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Lakeland, Florida! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a spacious 2,666 sqft of living space, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. The four bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy, with the master suite serving as a tranquil retreat. One of the highlights of this property is the versatile flex space, perfect for a home office, playroom, or additional bedroom. The flexibility of this space allows you to tailor it to your unique needs, making it an invaluable asset for any homeowner. Take advantage of not one, but two community resort-style pools, providing the perfect escape for relaxation and recreation. The community also features two playgrounds for the little ones and a dedicated dog park, ensuring that every member of the family, including your furry friends, can enjoy the great outdoors.
